  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【核心玩法特色】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三大修行模式 随心切换</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>正常模式</strong>：无拘无束拼合灵寰宝鉴，静心感悟天地灵气</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时限模式</strong>：倒计时急速拼图！手速与神识的终极试炼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>步数模式</strong>：限定步数内完成阵法，每一子皆暗合天道</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【多位仙子伴修】</strong>   </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集仙袂飘飘的修仙佳人，完成拼图即可解锁图鉴！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3577110/extras/d0533e8e5d043a2349c0a13bdd5b7973.avif?t=1748005756\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3577110/extras_big/d0533e8e5d043a2349c0a13bdd5b7973.avif?t=1748005756 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【视听禅境体验】</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐与精美拼图碎片组合杀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3577110/extras/4a508132161903f6af7bd1e7854c5aea.avif?t=1748005756\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3577110/extras_big/4a508132161903f6af7bd1e7854c5aea.avif?t=1748005756 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【轻松修仙 随时悟道】</strong>   </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需繁杂操作，指尖轻划即可，享受惬意人生</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3577110/extras/a41c3d1229131cf3cd1fd51e1d74fc90.avif?t=1748005756\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3577110/extras_big/a41c3d1229131cf3cd1fd51e1d74fc90.avif?t=1748005756 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【适宜人群】</strong>   <br>✔ 国风美学爱好者 ✔ 碎片时间休闲玩家   <br>✔ 轻度解谜挑战者 ✔ 修仙文化发烧友</p>",
